Beautiful pic!! I love this...so dark and moody yet beautiful. You won't believe me but I just finished getting my lighthouse pic I was going to use in this same challenge!!  must both still be trying to find our way! 

@jewelszee "lighthouse man I'm all at sea, shine your little lighthouse light on me". I'd believe it.  I have had some odd 'coincidences' like that elsewhere on IG ;) I like the moodiness of it too.  I am looking forward to seeing yours!!!

@robynbromley thankyou! I found it hard to pick for this challenge. I had probably another 5 others, maybe 7. I like my leaves shot best from my 5 I think. It reminds me of something - silence, childhood winters, a particular day when I played by myself in the leaves.  But I was really pleased with this one :)

caption.text: #mybestfive challenge. Okay - I try not to do reposts too often, as I don't want to repeat myself (says the girl who posts tree shots like she has some kind of sick compulsion). But I am reposting a couple in order to participate in the challenge being run by @Chrysti. Have a go yourself, it might be fun -  check out the schmick posts of others - already 100s of others up there. my pick are based on those that appeal to me, not necessarily those that are most liked by others. 
